The domain transfer process for .ai domains is similar to other extensions. You will need to unlock the domain at your registrar, obtain the authorisation code (EPP code), and provide it to the buyer. The buyer initiates the transfer at their registrar and the process typically takes 3-7 days.

Some high-value transactions use a domain holding service or an attorney to manage the transfer. For deals above $100,000, legal assistance is a good idea.

