### Sedo's Escrow and Transfer Service

Regardless of which transaction method is used, Sedo provides an integrated escrow service. The buyer deposits funds with Sedo, Sedo verifies the payment, the seller transfers the domain, Sedo confirms the transfer, and then releases the funds to the seller. This protects both parties from fraud, which is especially important when six-figure sums are involved.

