In any market, comparable sales ("comps") are how you establish fair value. The .ai domain market is maturing rapidly, and with 534+ verified sales tracked by NameBuzz, buyers and sellers now have a growing body of evidence to reference.

### How Comps Work in Domain Valuation

When someone lists "write.ai" for sale, a smart buyer does not just negotiate based on gut feeling. They look at what similar domains sold for:

